Recommends: timeshift, libreoffice-l10n-de, fonts-liberation
Description: Aptura OS everyday application set
 The daily-work software bundle: LibreOffice (office), Thunderbird (mail),
 Firefox (browser), GNOME Software with Flatpak/Flathub, backups, archives,
 multimedia codecs, firmware updates and printing. Spotify is installed as a
 Flatpak by the build hook (not available via APT).
 .
 Firefox is provided as a real .deb from the Mozilla APT repository configured
 by the build (not the Ubuntu snap transitional package).
